## Links and Navigation
- Always use the typed `<Link>` from `@tanstack/react-router`.
- Pass `to`, `params`, `activeProps`, and Tailwind classes, mirroring:  
  ```tsx
  <Link
    to="/posts/$postId"
    params={{ postId: post.id }}
    activeProps={{ className: 'text-black ...' }}
    className="block ..."
  >
    {post.title}
  </Link>
  ```